quran[22{c,v,t}:
85,1,Wassamaaa'i zaatil burooj
85,2,Wal yawmil maw'ood
85,3,Wa shaahidinw wa mashhood
85,4,Qutila as haabul ukhdood
85,5,Annaari zaatil waqood
85,6,Iz hum 'alaihaa qu'ood
85,7,Wa hum 'alaa maa yaf'aloona bilmu 'mineena shuhood
85,8,Wa maa naqamoo minhum illaaa aiyu'minoo billaahil 'azeezil Hameed
85,9,Allazee lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal ard; wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai 'in Shaheed
85,10,Innal lazeena fatanul mu'mineena wal mu'minaati summa lam yatooboo falahum 'azaabu Jahannama wa lahum 'azaabul hareeq
85,11,Innal lazeena aamanoo wa 'amilus saalihaati lahum Jannaatun tajree min tahtihal anhaar; zaalikal fawzul kabeer
85,12,Inna batsha Rabbika lashadeed
85,13,Innahoo Huwa yubdi'u wa yu'eed
85,14,Wa Huwal Ghafoorul Wadood
85,15,Zul 'Arshil Majeed
85,16,Fa' 'aalul limaa yureed
85,17,Hal ataaka hadeesul junood
85,18,Fir'awna wa Samood
85,19,Balil lazeena kafaroo fee takzeeb
85,20,Wallaahu minw waraaa'ihim muheet
85,21,Bal huwa Quraanum Majeed
85,22,Fee Lawhim Mahfooz
